SDK installation Steps:
1) Download scala-SDK-3.0.3-2.10-linux.gtk.x86_64.tar.gz
2) Extact the contents and this creates the folder eclipse
3) cd eclipse
4)./eclipse ( in terminal )
5) This opens the scala IDE and prompts you for workspace. Specify the workspace directory.
6) The IDE allows to create java as well as scala projects.
